#: ../source/notebooks/mmm/mmm_allocation_assessment.ipynb:170004
#: a374ce73001448a5a7fd426f706f6f46
msgid ""
"Based on this, using the optimized allocation its very likely to get a "
"respose of 145,255 units sold but also the budget could bring as low as "
"125,000 units sold or as big as 162,000 units sold. On the other hand, "
"using the guessed allocation its very likely to get a respose of 123,000 "
"units sold but also the budget could bring as low as 117,000 units sold "
"or as big as 133,000 units sold."
